<i>and the best of luck.</i>

26:33.258 --> 26:35.302
<i>Hello, I'm actress Lee Young-ae.</i>

26:35.760 --> 26:39.556
<i>I'd like to congratulate all of you</i>
<i>on your admission.</i>

26:39.639 --> 26:41.391
LEE YOUNG-AE
German (1990 FRESHMAN)

26:41.516 --> 26:44.894
