if you'd like me to carry that for you.

27:39.199 --> 27:41.576
No, it's okay. Thanks, Won-ho.

27:42.202 --> 27:44.996
-You remember my name?
-Of course. You're Jang Won-ho.

27:45.205 --> 27:47.874
You had a nice voice
when you said hi to me earlier.

27:49.918 --> 27:51.920
Do you not remember my name?

27:52.379 --> 27:54.964
What are you talking about?
Of course I remember.

27:55.256 --> 27:57.217
You're Sua. Hyun Sua.

27:57.842 --> 27:59.803
You have good memory.

28:00.136 --> 28:04.099
Gosh, don't waste your time.
I'm sure she's fussy about guys.

28:04.182 --> 28:06.351
Are you talking about me? That's not true.

28:06.476 --> 28:08.478
Everyone says that.

28:08.937 --> 28:11.564
I'm telling the truth.
Why would you think that way?

28:11.648 --> 28:13.024
Just bring that over.

28:16.569 --> 28:18.988
Gosh, he's so good-looking.

28:19.364 --> 28:21.366
He's extremely handsome.

28:21.991 --> 28:24.452
What? Yes, you're right.

28:29.165 --> 28:31.459
I'm Ko Ye-na, and I'm a sophomore.

28:33.044 --> 28:35.880
I really like watching movies.

28:38.007 --> 28:40.844
And I can always treat you to a meal,
so call me.

28:40.969 --> 28:41.886
Next.

28:43.596 --> 28:45.974
Hello, I'm Noh Min-ah, a sophomore.

28:47.892 --> 28:50.270
Hello, I'm Song Jung-ho, a sophomore.

28:52.981 --> 28:55.692
I'm Kim Chan-woo.
I entered this university in 2013.

28:55.859 --> 28:58.903
I may be hard to approach
as I'm way older than you,

28:59.320 --> 29:03.908
but you can always come to me
if you need advice.

29:07.746 --> 29:10.665
Lastly, I'm Koo Tae-young,
the student president.

29:10.749 --> 29:13.334
I'd like to welcome you all
to the chemistry department.

29:16.838 --> 29:19.883
Now, the freshmen can start
introducing themselves.

29:20.091 --> 29:21.342
Please come out.

29:22.302 --> 29:25.180
-I'm so nervous to introduce myself.
-Me too.

29:35.607 --> 29:37.108
I'm Do Kyung-seok.

29:37.859 --> 29:39.486
<i>Do Kyung-seok?</i>

29:41.946 --> 29:44.574
I like working out, and I like drinking.

29:44.824 --> 29:46.284
Call me when you drink.

29:46.367 --> 29:48.119
-You're good-looking.
-How handsome.

29:52.457 --> 29:56.044
<i>No way.</i>
<i>He can't be the Do Kyung-seok I know.</i>

30:02.842 --> 30:03.885
That's enough.

30:05.011 --> 30:06.805
I'm really nervous.

30:07.388 --> 30:10.058
Hello, I'm Hyun Sua, a freshman.

30:10.266 --> 30:11.935
She's the prettiest girl.

30:12.018 --> 30:14.354
She's going to be the most popular girl
this year.

30:15.563 --> 30:18.566
I know it's important
to study hard as a university student,

30:18.650 --> 30:21.319
but I also want to make a lot of friends.

30:21.820 --> 30:24.322
I hope we can all get along well.

30:24.572 --> 30:25.865
I'll become your friend.

30:25.949 --> 30:27.742
Let's be good friends.

30:28.159 --> 30:30.912
I have a question.
Do you have a boyfriend?

30:31.037 --> 30:34.624
No, I don't. This is embarrassing,
but I've never dated anyone before.

30:34.707 --> 30:37.794
-Come on. Don't lie.
-No way.

30:37.877 --> 30:39.546
-Such a lie.
-Unbelievable.

30:39.629 --> 30:41.130
No way. That can't be true.

30:42.048 --> 30:45.468
The next girl is really pretty,
so I'll just end it here.

30:46.886 --> 30:48.888
Mi-rae, it's your turn.

30:49.347 --> 30:50.265
Me?

30:54.102 --> 30:56.563
Okay, let's move
onto the next pretty girl.

30:56.855 --> 30:58.106
<i>The next pretty girl?</i>

30:59.023 --> 31:01.484
<i>That makes it sound like</i>
<i>I'm as pretty as her.</i>

31:06.406 --> 31:08.449
I've never seen a girl
with plastic surgery done.

31:08.908 --> 31:11.035
I like girls like her.

31:13.955 --> 31:16.332
<i>I'm so nervous.</i>

31:17.375 --> 31:19.711
Hello, I'm Kang Mi-rae.

31:26.175 --> 31:28.636
I also hope that we'll all get along.

31:29.012 --> 31:30.138
Do you have a boyfriend?

31:30.763 --> 31:33.141
-No.
-Come on.

31:33.224 --> 31:34.058
Let's be honest.

31:34.809 --> 31:36.311
I really don't have one.

31:36.436 --> 31:38.688
Do girls think
those kind of faces are pretty?

31:41.190 --> 31:43.443
I look forward to
getting to know all of you.

31:49.282 --> 31:50.575
It's nice to meet you.

31:51.534 --> 31:53.661
Let's move onto the next pretty girl.

31:54.037 --> 31:54.871
Who's next?

31:58.416 --> 31:59.584
Come on. Cheers.

31:59.667 --> 32:01.336
-Cheers.
-Cheers. You too.

32:01.586 --> 32:03.379
Sua, which part do you like?

32:03.463 --> 32:04.881
-Do you like drumsticks?
-Me?

32:04.964 --> 32:06.341
Let's see. Here's one.

32:07.634 --> 32:09.636
-Here you go, Sua.
-No, it's okay.

32:09.886 --> 32:11.095
Can you drink, Sua?

32:11.179 --> 32:14.057
Yes, I can. Let me pour you a drink first.

32:14.599 --> 32:17.060
-Thanks.
-What's she doing?

32:19.103 --> 32:20.480
I'll pour you a drink, too.

32:20.563 --> 32:22.148
Gosh, thank you.

32:22.565 --> 32:23.983
You can call me casually.

32:24.359 --> 32:26.819
Give me that. I'll pour you a drink, too.

32:26.903 --> 32:27.987
Thank you.

32:28.071 --> 32:29.989
She seems to have a great personality.

32:30.073 --> 32:32.241
I know. She's really friendly.

32:32.951 --> 32:34.786
-Let's all clink our glasses.
-Okay.

32:34.869 --> 32:37.205
-Welcome.
-Bottoms up.

32:37.288 --> 32:40.083
-Cheers.
-Let's do this.

32:40.959 --> 32:43.503
-What did you do after taking the CSAT?
-I had fun.

32:43.586 --> 32:45.838
-With your girlfriend?
-No.

32:47.674 --> 32:49.217
Don't you have a girlfriend?

32:50.009 --> 32:51.886
-No.
-Did you break up with her?

32:51.970 --> 32:53.638
When did you break up with her?

32:55.181 --> 32:56.474
I'm not interested in girls.

32:57.976 --> 32:59.811
Do you drink well?

32:59.894 --> 33:02.063
I enjoy drinking. What about you?

33:25.753 --> 33:26.838
<i>It's him.</i>

33:27.964 --> 33:29.424
<i>I think it's him.</i>

33:32.260 --> 33:34.429
Mi-rae, I envy you so much.

33:34.679 --> 33:37.390
-What?
-Your name is as pretty as your face.

33:38.141 --> 33:40.893
My name is Jung-boon. It's so tacky.

33:41.436 --> 33:43.229
<i>How am I supposed to respond to this?</i>

33:43.312 --> 33:45.189
<i>What am I supposed to say?</i>

33:45.273 --> 33:47.400
No, you're prettier. Don't say that.

33:47.483 --> 33:50.486
Gosh, come on. That's too big of a lie.

33:50.695 --> 33:53.656
You look like an actress. Right?

33:54.073 --> 33:56.075
You kind of look like an announcer, too.

33:57.702 --> 34:01.247
Can you guys drink?
We should start drinking as well.

34:01.330 --> 34:02.373
Okay.

34:03.750 --> 34:04.625
What?

34:05.126 --> 34:08.295
-What?
-What's this?

34:08.755 --> 34:12.341
How dare a freshman drink water?

34:13.176 --> 34:16.304
If I catch you acting all shy,
I'm going to have to scold you.

34:16.387 --> 34:17.221
So manly.

34:17.304 --> 34:19.264
-Let's fill our glasses.
-Let's do it.

34:19.348 --> 34:22.226
Yours is empty.
Jung-boon, I'll pour you a glass.

34:24.937 --> 34:25.772
Mi-rae, you too.

34:27.857 --> 34:30.234
Here we go. Bottoms up.

34:35.156 --> 34:37.324
Mi-rae,
do you really not have a boyfriend?

34:38.034 --> 34:39.744
What? No.

34:41.286 --> 34:43.414
Then can I be your boyfriend?

34:44.040 --> 34:44.873
Pardon?

34:46.918 --> 34:49.337
<i>♪ Love, love, love ♪</i>

34:49.545 --> 34:50.379
Bam!

34:50.505 --> 34:52.757
You're not as energetic as you used to be.

34:52.840 --> 34:54.300
Let's all fill our glasses.

34:54.382 --> 34:56.385
-Let's fill them up.
-Pour the drinks.

34:57.303 --> 35:00.306
Now, it's time for the games.

35:02.809 --> 35:04.102
<i>Ready, go.</i>

35:04.519 --> 35:08.648
<i>-Kim Sung-woon!</i>
<i>-Kim Sung-woon!</i>

35:09.065 --> 35:12.777
<i>-Kim Sung-woon!</i>
<i>-Kim Sung-woon!</i>

35:19.700 --> 35:21.661
Do Kyung-seok, you can do it!

35:26.582 --> 35:28.334
Wow!

35:28.626 --> 35:30.753
Do Kyung-seok!

35:31.879 --> 35:33.881
<i>Even if he's that Kyung-seok,</i>
<i>so what?</i>

35:34.423 --> 35:36.425
<i>He won't recognize me anyway.</i>

35:38.177 --> 35:39.137
Let's do it again.

35:39.887 --> 35:40.930
Finish drinking.

35:43.224 --> 35:46.310
-"Starry Night" by Mamamoo.
-"Starry Night" by Mamamoo!

35:46.435 --> 35:48.437
Correct, Choi Jung-boon!

35:52.150 --> 35:53.734
"Don't Know You" by Heize.

35:53.818 --> 35:55.987
Me! The answer is
"Don't Know You" by Heize.

35:56.362 --> 35:58.865
-Correct.
-What's with her?

36:07.582 --> 36:09.041
"Road Fighter" by Sechs Kies.

36:09.333 --> 36:10.877
"Road Fighter" by Sechs Kies.

36:13.171 --> 36:15.923
-Bingo. Oh, my.
-My goodness.

36:16.007 --> 36:17.717
My gosh, how did she know?

36:19.844 --> 36:22.805
-"Bboom Bboom" by Momoland.
-"Bboong Bboong" by Momoland!

36:22.889 --> 36:24.932
Again.
The pronunciation has to be precise.

36:25.057 --> 36:26.392
"Bboong Bboong."

36:26.475 --> 36:28.603
Wrong. It's not a fart.
What's the song?

36:28.686 --> 36:30.271
"Bboom Bboom"!

36:30.354 --> 36:34.775
Correct. Now, it's dance time, everyone!

36:43.868 --> 36:45.494
-Wi-Fi.
-Correct!

36:46.412 --> 36:48.414
Senior Koo Tae-young,
you got the correct answer.

36:51.834 --> 36:53.836
-Final exam.
-Final exam, correct!

36:54.337 --> 36:56.339
Congratulation!
Next.

36:56.756 --> 36:59.634
-Me! "The pot calling the kettle black."
-Bingo!

37:02.011 --> 37:03.304
Pass.

37:03.846 --> 37:05.473
Gosh, wrong. Wrong answer!

37:06.182 --> 37:09.644
-Mirror.
-Looks like I'm looking at myself?

37:13.272 --> 37:15.524
Give me a big hand for all the hard work!

37:18.152 --> 37:20.446
NATURAL SCIENCE DIVISION
AT HANKOOK UNIVERSITY

37:22.782 --> 37:24.617
The winning team at the moment is...

37:27.828 --> 37:30.248
Team 1 and Team 3 are
in first place together.

37:34.502 --> 37:38.547
The final match will be a talent
competition between the team leaders.

37:42.551 --> 37:44.220
-Me?
-Yes.

37:44.303 --> 37:46.305
You guessed all the songs correctly.

37:46.389 --> 37:48.557
I saw you could dance like this.

37:48.641 --> 37:53.020
She did?
My goodness, you must've partied a lot.

37:54.563 --> 37:56.774
Kang Mi-rae, you will be our team leader.

37:58.359 --> 38:00.361
No, I can't do things like that.

38:00.444 --> 38:02.780
-Don't worry. Just do it.
-Yes.

38:02.905 --> 38:06.993
-Kang Mi-rae, Kang Mi-rae!
-Kang Mi-rae, Kang Mi-rae!

38:07.576 --> 38:10.663
What should I do? They want me to dance
as the team's leader.

38:10.955 --> 38:13.457
<i>Then you must do your best</i>
<i>as the team leader.</i>

38:13.541 --> 38:14.959
No...

38:15.626 --> 38:18.045
Why does it have to be me? Why me?

38:18.337 --> 38:20.256
<i>You're a great dancer.</i>

38:20.339 --> 38:22.591
You couldn't resist flaunting your talent.

38:22.675 --> 38:25.678
Whatever happened already happened,
and you're a team leader.

38:25.761 --> 38:27.430
You must give it your all.

38:27.513 --> 38:31.392
If you get shy and don't do your best,
they will think that you're acting coy.

38:31.475 --> 38:34.270
With that face,
it'll come across as so obnoxious.

38:34.729 --> 38:37.523
I just want to run away.

38:37.690 --> 38:39.650
<i>Hey, Kang Mi-rae.</i>

38:39.734 --> 38:42.111
Don't be such a coward, okay?

38:42.236 --> 38:44.947
Nothing will change
if you keep avoiding challenges.

38:45.740 --> 38:47.742
<i>You don't want to live like you used to.</i>

38:48.659 --> 38:51.454
<i>You finally have the chance</i>
<i>to flaunt your charms, girl.</i>

38:51.537 --> 38:53.497
Show them what you've got.

38:57.084 --> 38:58.127
Will I...

39:00.880 --> 39:02.465
be able to do a good job?

39:02.631 --> 39:04.842
Of course. You're my friend after all.

39:04.925 --> 39:07.428
Go and have as much fun as you want.

39:07.636 --> 39:11.766
"This is how you should dance.
I am Kang Mi-rae, the dancing queen."

39:11.849 --> 39:13.392
Show them what you can do.

39:18.397 --> 39:20.983
I have to go.

39:21.734 --> 39:26.155
Hey, actually, I have to rap
as a leader of my team as well.

39:27.114 --> 39:29.784
Let's talk later. Peace.

41:33.949 --> 41:35.034
KANG MI-RAE

41:54.345 --> 41:56.222
<i>I wanted to show people</i>

41:57.348 --> 41:58.807
<i>that I can do a good job too.</i>

42:27.211 --> 42:29.046
<i>I wanted to show everyone.</i>

42:29.171 --> 42:31.173
-Kang Mi-rae!
-Kang Mi-rae!

42:31.298 --> 42:32.883
<i>Like everyone else,</i>

42:34.093 --> 42:35.886
<i>I wanted to be loved.</i>

42:35.970 --> 42:38.889
-Kang Mi-rae!
-Kang Mi-rae!

42:39.098 --> 42:40.432
<i>I wanted to</i>

42:42.268 --> 42:44.228
<i>be loved in an ordinary way.</i>

42:44.478 --> 42:47.231
-Kang Mi-rae!
-Kang Mi-rae!

42:50.776 --> 42:52.152
For Mi-rae!

42:52.278 --> 42:53.404
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

42:53.779 --> 42:55.447
Gosh, Mi-rae is so cool.

43:00.160 --> 43:02.913
Mi-rae, you're awesome.
You're like an idol singer.

43:03.205 --> 43:07.543
-Were you in a dance club?
-No, I practiced alone by watching TV.

43:08.085 --> 43:09.837
It's even more impressive then.

43:10.212 --> 43:13.674
Whatever. Let's drink a shot
with our arms crossed, Mi-rae.

43:17.761 --> 43:20.556
-Do it.
-Do it.

43:20.639 --> 43:22.808
-Do it.
-Hurry.

43:22.891 --> 43:25.519
-Do it.
-Do it.

43:26.312 --> 43:28.314
-Do it.
-Do it.

43:28.606 --> 43:30.608
Here. Like this.

43:30.899 --> 43:33.569
Mi-rae of the chemistry department is
our MVP!

43:33.736 --> 43:34.612
Mi-rae.

43:35.904 --> 43:38.616
It seems like
she's too drunk to drink.

43:40.159 --> 43:41.327
Please excuse me.

43:43.704 --> 43:46.332
How dare she try to act weak
in front of her senior?

43:47.041 --> 43:49.501
How about we do it together instead?

43:49.918 --> 43:50.878
Oh, no.

44:17.279 --> 44:19.281
I wish they wouldn't make me drink.

44:41.470 --> 44:45.099
-Kang Mi-rae!
-Kang Mi-rae!

44:45.182 --> 44:49.186
-Kang Mi-rae!
-Kang Mi-rae!

45:17.589 --> 45:18.882
Hi, Mom.

45:19.883 --> 45:21.635
What's wrong? Did something happen?

45:24.304 --> 45:25.848
Mom...

45:33.272 --> 45:34.940
Nothing.

45:36.066 --> 45:37.735
I'm having fun.

45:39.194 --> 45:42.322
People like me, Mom.

45:44.783 --> 45:47.870
I got startled. I thought
something happened to you.

45:48.954 --> 45:49.830
Really?

45:51.832 --> 45:54.042
I'm happy that you're having fun.

45:57.171 --> 46:01.550
<i>I'm getting a call.</i>
<i>Have fun. I'll call you again later.</i>

46:21.445 --> 46:24.740
Gosh, I shouldn't cry,
or my eyes will get red.

46:44.176 --> 46:47.763
You're really good at drinking.
Did you start in high school?

46:52.226 --> 46:53.227
That's cool.

46:55.479 --> 46:58.941
Don't you think it's a little hot in here?

46:59.650 --> 47:01.860
How about we go out for some fresh air?

47:03.070 --> 47:04.112
You can go alone.

47:12.538 --> 47:13.539
Where are you going?

47:14.998 --> 47:16.124
To get some fresh air.

47:20.879 --> 47:22.047
He's chic.

47:32.015 --> 47:34.434
You were really good at drinking
back there.

47:42.526 --> 47:43.652
Sorry.

47:44.027 --> 47:45.487
I think I'm drunk.

47:49.616 --> 47:51.618
I'm so foolish, don't you think?

47:52.244 --> 47:54.246
I get drunk after only a few shots.

47:57.791 --> 47:58.625
Excuse me.

48:03.171 --> 48:05.132
Does anyone have anything to sober her up?

48:05.924 --> 48:07.259
She says she's drunk.

48:11.513 --> 48:13.307
-Sua.
-Drink this.

48:13.390 --> 48:15.559
-It's best for sobering up.
-Get on my back.

48:15.642 --> 48:18.145
-I'll carry you on my back.
-It's really effective.

48:18.228 --> 48:19.104
Drink this.

49:07.819 --> 49:08.779
<i>What are you doing?</i>

49:08.862 --> 49:09.947
FROM: HYUN-JUNG

49:10.030 --> 49:11.114
<i>I'm outside.</i>

49:11.782 --> 49:14.201
<i>They keep telling me to drink</i>
<i>when I'm in there.</i>

49:16.620 --> 49:18.622
<i>Do you remember Do Kyung-seok?</i>

49:19.206 --> 49:20.707
<i>In our department...</i>

49:21.333 --> 49:22.167
Oh my gosh!

49:24.169 --> 49:25.045
<i>Hello?</i>

49:35.013 --> 49:36.139
<i>Hello?</i>

49:40.060 --> 49:41.311
<i>Hello?</i>

49:42.229 --> 49:44.231
I'm sure I called my daughter's number.

49:45.607 --> 49:46.817
Who's there?

49:47.442 --> 49:48.860
Oh, well...

49:51.738 --> 49:54.157
I'm Mi-rae's senior.

49:55.909 --> 49:59.579
<i>I see.</i>
<i>Why do you have her phone by the way?</i>

49:59.746 --> 50:01.039
Well, that's...

50:03.458 --> 50:06.503
Freshmen are not allowed to use
their phones during the event.

50:06.586 --> 50:08.547
So we collected them for the time being.

50:08.880 --> 50:10.882
<i>Oh, I see.</i>

50:11.967 --> 50:13.885
<i>-I'm sorry.</i>
-Not at all.

50:15.929 --> 50:16.930
I'm sorry.

50:17.014 --> 50:19.307
<i>It's okay.</i>
<i>Well, goodbye then.</i>

50:23.729 --> 50:25.188
Dad...

50:33.447 --> 50:36.324
You're home early.
Have you eaten dinner?

50:38.994 --> 50:41.580
What's wrong? Did something happen?

50:42.497 --> 50:44.499
She was just like Mi-rae.

50:46.918 --> 50:49.671
Did you talk to her on the phone?

50:49.755 --> 50:53.300
She looked pretty with round eyes
and a sharp nose.

50:54.217 --> 50:56.803
Well, that's...

50:57.596 --> 51:00.057
Ever since she graduated middle school,

51:00.599 --> 51:03.101
she wanted to do a plastic surgery
on her eyelids.

51:03.185 --> 51:04.144
What?

51:04.227 --> 51:06.813
She got so stressed out
because of her face.

51:06.897 --> 51:08.523
There you go again.

51:09.357 --> 51:12.486
What's wrong with her face
that you keep stirring up her mind?

51:12.903 --> 51:14.071
I already said no.

51:15.405 --> 51:17.699
Did I mishear because I miss my daughter?

51:18.033 --> 51:20.577
Her female senior took my call.

51:21.995 --> 51:23.997
Her voice sounded exactly like Mi-rae's.

51:25.248 --> 51:26.583
No way.

51:28.251 --> 51:30.253
She should've visited us first.

51:30.337 --> 51:32.923
Why did she have to go straight
to the orientation?

51:48.814 --> 51:49.815
Are you okay?

51:50.774 --> 51:51.650
What?

51:54.569 --> 51:55.445
Well...

51:57.572 --> 51:58.990
I'm okay.

51:59.908 --> 52:01.451
I just feel a little sick.

52:04.162 --> 52:05.080
Drink this.

52:08.667 --> 52:10.001
Thank you.

52:21.179 --> 52:23.223
Do you want to go rest
if you're too drunk?

52:23.348 --> 52:26.017
You might have to drink again
if you go back inside.

52:26.434 --> 52:28.436
There's a lounge with a sofa over there.

52:30.480 --> 52:32.232
Is there a place like that?

52:33.567 --> 52:34.776
Thank you.

52:46.079 --> 52:47.789
What are you waiting for?
Let's go.

53:44.054 --> 53:45.555
I should get some rest, too.

53:51.603 --> 53:54.481
Why are you standing there? Sit down.

53:58.276 --> 53:59.110
Okay.

54:15.835 --> 54:17.170
Aren't you uncomfortable?

54:17.837 --> 54:19.506
Sit down here comfortably.

54:20.924 --> 54:21.841
I'm okay.

54:23.593 --> 54:25.637
Why? Do I make you feel uncomfortable?

54:26.221 --> 54:28.223
Should we switch?
I'll sit over there.

54:28.348 --> 54:30.141
No, there's no need.

54:31.309 --> 54:32.560
Then I'll sit here.

54:58.211 --> 55:00.505
You're very pretty.

55:05.635 --> 55:06.928
Are you okay?

55:08.096 --> 55:09.097
I'm okay.

55:12.642 --> 55:14.352
I'm curious.

55:15.478 --> 55:17.105
Do you really not have a boyfriend?

55:19.065 --> 55:21.067
-No.
-Why?

55:23.069 --> 55:25.447
I just don't have one.

55:26.197 --> 55:27.032
I see.

55:34.080 --> 55:35.832
Then is it okay if  I like you?

55:36.291 --> 55:38.501
Looking at you playing games
and dancing earlier,

55:39.586 --> 55:41.129
I fell in love.

55:46.051 --> 55:48.553
<i>Is this a confession?</i>

55:50.930 --> 55:52.849
Don't think too seriously about it though.

55:57.354 --> 55:58.688
Oh, right.

56:00.106 --> 56:03.443
People might look for me
if I stay gone for too long.

56:07.197 --> 56:08.323
Who?

56:12.118 --> 56:15.372
No one else is more interested
in you than I am.

56:20.835 --> 56:22.921
They're busy having fun,

56:24.255 --> 56:25.215
so don't bother.

56:38.895 --> 56:39.813
Hey.

56:40.939 --> 56:42.941
Help me up already!

56:51.366 --> 56:53.493
What are you doing?

56:53.827 --> 56:54.911
What are you doing?

56:58.164 --> 56:59.541
It's none of your business.

57:01.000 --> 57:04.045
You came this way,
so I wondered what kind of place it was.

57:06.005 --> 57:08.258
What do you mean? It's no special place.

57:09.008 --> 57:12.595
She seemed too drunk, so I took her
so that she could rest for a while.

57:14.848 --> 57:17.142
Why did you open the door
when I was leaning on it?

57:19.519 --> 57:20.979
You were blocking the door.

57:25.859 --> 57:26.693
Are you drunk?

57:27.777 --> 57:29.779
Look at you being rude to your senior.

57:35.827 --> 57:38.830
I'm letting it go
because you're drunk, all right?

57:43.877 --> 57:44.961
Mi-rae. Let's go.

58:08.818 --> 58:09.736
Are you okay?

58:12.155 --> 58:14.824
Yes, I'm good.

58:22.040 --> 58:24.667
Rest here if you want to.

58:34.761 --> 58:35.887
Kang Mi-rae.

58:51.528 --> 58:52.529
By any chance,

58:55.073 --> 58:56.824
did you go to Jaryong Middle School?

59:07.877 --> 59:08.753
What?

59:26.563 --> 59:28.898
<i>Kyung-seok treats you differently</i>
<i>from others.</i>

59:28.982 --> 59:30.441
<i>Do you go out with him?</i>

59:30.525 --> 59:32.652
-She's already so famous.
-She's so pretty.

59:32.735 --> 59:33.653
Mi-rae.

59:33.736 --> 59:36.573
You and Mi-rae might get along
with each other very well,

59:36.656 --> 59:38.199
though I feel a little bad.

59:38.283 --> 59:40.034
I haven't done any plastic surgery.

59:40.118 --> 59:41.703
Mi-rae hasn't either.

59:41.786 --> 59:42.996
You think it's funny?

59:43.121 --> 59:44.539
Do you go to this university?

59:44.747 --> 59:46.207
I'm your daughter, Mi-rae.

59:46.708 --> 59:48.710
Gosh, you plastic monster.

59:49.043 --> 59:50.461
What have I done?

59:50.628 --> 59:53.339
Do you have a crush on him?

59:57.844 --> 59:59.846
